hamonikr-chatbot (1.1.2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add CLI option -p/--prompt to send an initial request and show response on startup
  * Add CLI option -c/--clipboard to use clipboard content as the initial request
    - Tries xclip, then xsel (3 attempts); ignored if clipboard is empty
  * Update launchers to pass through CLI args (src/bavarder.in, src/hamonikr-chatbot-launcher.in)

